Location (\(y\))

  • L1
  • L2/3

Predictors

  • Type of source corpus (press/internet)
  • Activation state – length of the subject (long / short)
  • Presentational head verb (yes / no)
  • Which adverbial (Y, LW, LY)
  • Language (fi / ru)

Interactions

  • Finnish + press / internet
  • Finnish + long / short
  • Finnish + yes / no
